rows.label: qst650411_msg0001
rows.name: I wonder what's happened there...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0002
rows.name: We should try and find out.

rows.label: qst650411_msg0003
rows.name:
Hey there, little one.
What's the matter?

rows.label: qst650411_msg0004
rows.name:
My ma and da went out and they've
been gone a long time and now I'm
worried, and, and, and...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0005
rows.name:
I gotcha, little lady.
We'll go and look for them, okay?

rows.label: qst650411_msg0006
rows.name: No, you don't get it...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0007
rows.name:
I'm just really, really hungry now!
And when I'm hungry I just get so sad...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0008
rows.name: O-oh. I see...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0009
rows.name:
Well, shall we see what you've got
in the larder? I'm sure we could whip
you up a quick snack if we tried.

rows.label: qst650411_msg0010
rows.name: Would you really?!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0011
rows.name: Sure!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0012
rows.name:
Shouldn't be too much trouble,
right, Nia?

rows.label: qst650411_msg0013
rows.name: No objections here.

rows.label: qst650411_msg0014
rows.name: Okay! Come on inside, then!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0101
rows.name: Homura, you're... You're...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0102
rows.name: You're my hero!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0103
rows.name:
You didn't even know that little girl,
but you still went and cooked her
a feast...!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0104
rows.name:
Oh, it was nothing, really.
We couldn't have left her crying there...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0105
rows.name:
That's our Homura, always a champion
of the people.

rows.label: qst650411_msg0106
rows.name:
She sure is! And she shines brighter
than any sparkler!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0107
rows.name:
Not the comparison I'd have gone with
myself, but okay...

rows.label: qst650411_msg0108
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I'll do whatever it takes so that I can
be just like my hero some day!

rows.label: qst650411_msg0109
rows.name:
O-oh, that's...nice.
Let me know what I can do to help.
